message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.BIO, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a model using convolutional neural network for medical diagnosis based on plantar pressure data. This involves the use of computer vision techniques (cs.CV) and machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) to learn representations from the data. The application of the model is in the field of healthcare (cs.HC) and specifically in medical diagnosis (cs.BIO). Additionally, the use of neural networks for medical diagnosis is a topic of interest in the field of neuroscience (cs.NEURON).
